OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FThe former Sunderland South MP, Chris
OL,8,FMullin, has been knighted in the
OL,9,FKing's Birthday Honours List.
OL,11,FSir Chris, 78, served his constituents
OL,12,Fbetween 1987 and 2010, as well as
OL,13,Fbeing a junior minister in Sir Tony
OL,14,FBlair's government. He later published
OL,15,Fa series of diaries from his time in
OL,16,Fgovernment, which became bestsellers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
