OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FHe has also written four novels,
OL,8,Fincluding A Very British Coup, which
OL,9,Fportrays the undermining of a left-
OL,10,Fwing government. Having previously
OL,11,Fworked as a journalist, he told ITV
OL,12,FNews Tyne Tees his proudest moment
OL,13,Ffrom that time was the key role he
OL,14,Fplayed in helping secure the release
OL,15,Fof the Birmingham Six, a group of men
OL,16,Fwrongly convicted of the IRA's pub
OL,17,Fbombings in the city in 1974.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FHe said: "It took quite a big fight
OL,8,Fwith the legal establishment and the
OL,9,Fpolitical establishment before we won,
OL,10,Fand that Royal Commission was
OL,11,Fsubsequently set up, in fact it was
OL,12,Fset up on the day that the Birmingham
OL,13,FSix were released, and that led to
OL,14,Fvarious reforms to the judicial system
OL,15,Fand it led to the quashing of a great
OL,16,Fmany other wrongful convictions."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
