FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FReminiscing about his time in
OL,8,FSunderland, he added: "It's nice to be
OL,9,Fremembered. I found Sunderland a
OL,10,Fwonderful place to represent and some
OL,11,Fof my colleagues, on getting elected,
OL,12,Fmoved immediately to London and just
OL,13,Fpopped up to their constituencies, but
OL,14,FI lived there throughout and I was
OL,15,Fvery glad to do so."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
