PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FAlso knighted is the world leading
OL,8,FDurham University cosmologist,
OL,9,FProfessor Sir Carlos Frenk. He is one
OL,10,Fof the originators of the Cold Dark
OL,11,FMatter theory for the formation of
OL,12,Fstructure in the Universe.
OL,14,FSir Carlos said in a statement the it
OL,15,Fwould be an understatement to say he
OL,16,Fis "overjoyed" and that it's a
OL,17,F"tremendous honour".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
