CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FYasmin Khan of the Halo Project
OL,8,Fbecomes a CBE for her work on ending
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse and violence against
OL,10,Fwomen.
OL,12,FShe told ITV News: "I think this is a
OL,13,Frecognition to the survivors and the
OL,14,Fvictims, and it recognises the
OL,15,Fimportance of charities like Halo, and
OL,16,Fof course, the work that we do to make
OL,17,Fsure that women are safe and that they
OL,18,Fare protected."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
