PN,42108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1781352682
OL,3,CFormer Sunderland South MP and
OL,4,Cpolitical diarist, Chris Mullin,
OL,5,CKnighted
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News he said: "I was
OL,8,Fjust really excited that I was going
OL,9,Fto be able to talk to all of the
OL,10,Forganisations that I am involved in
OL,11,Fand just make clear to them that
OL,12,Factually this is their's as well as
OL,13,Fmine and that they should feel really
OL,14,Fproud and I really want to spur them
OL,15,Fon to do even more of the great work
OL,16,Fthat they already do."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
